<h2><span class="small-icon home-icon"></span>Home</h2>
{{#Model.ShowWelcome}}
<div class="call-to-action" id="intro">
  <a href="#" class="close-intro" title="Close">Close</a>
  <h2>Welcome to BowerBird, {{Model.User.Name}}!</h2>
  <p>Now that you have joined, please take the time to have a look at the introduction to familiarise yourself with BowerBird.</p>

  <h3>Projects</h3>
  <p>
    A project is a group of people with a common goal or interests in making sightings. You will find lots of projects you can join by clicking the Projects link above. 
  </p>
  <h3>Sightings</h3>
  <p>
    A sighting is an observation or a record of something you have seen. It consists of a title, a combination of photos, video and audio and a location. If you are a member of a project, you can add your observation to that project so that other members can view, discuss and identify your contribution. And that's just the start!
  </p>
  <h3>Learn More</h3>
  <p>There's a lot more to BowerBird than meets the eye. <a href="#">Learn more here</a></p>
</div>
{{/Model.ShowWelcome}}
<div class="tab-bar large">
  <ul class="tabs">
    <li>
      <a class="tab-button activities-tab-button {{#Model.ShowActivities}}selected{{/Model.ShowActivities}}" href="/">Activity</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="tab-button sightings-tab-button {{#Model.ShowSightings}}selected{{/Model.ShowSightings}}" href="/sightings">Sightings</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="tab-button posts-tab-button {{#Model.ShowPosts}}selected{{/Model.ShowPosts}}" href="/posts">Posts</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
<div class="details">
  {{#Model.ShowActivities}}
  <div class="stream">
    {{>Stream}}
  </div>
  {{/Model.ShowActivities}}
  {{#Model.ShowSightings}}
  <div class="sightings">
    {{>SightingList}}
  </div>
  {{/Model.ShowSightings}}
  {{#Model.ShowPosts}}
  <div class="posts">
    {{>PostsList}}
  </div>
  {{/Model.ShowPosts}}
</div>
